{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "NexoCRM API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for NexoCRM.\n\n**Base URL:** `http://localhost:8080/api/v1`\n\n**Auth:** Tokens are set as httpOnly cookies on login/onboard. Postman handles cookies automatically.\n\n**Tenant:** Send `x-tenant-slug` header on every authenticated request.\n\n**RBAC roles (lowest → highest):** `viewer → sales_rep → manager → admin → owner`\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set collection variables: `NEXOURL`, `tenantSlug`, `email`\n2. Run `POST /auth/onboard` to create tenant + owner\n3. Run `POST /auth/login` — cookies are set automatically\n4. All subsequent requests use those cookies + `x-tenant-slug` header",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "NEXOURL", "value": "http://localhost:8080/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "tenantSlug", "value": "acme", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "email", "value": "owner@acme.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "contact_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "pipeline_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "history_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "activity_key", "value": "demo", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "entity", "value": "contacts", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "invite_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "reset_token", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Authentication endpoints. Public endpoints need no cookies.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Onboarding",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/onboard",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "onboard"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"businessName\": \"Acme Corp\",\n  \"slug\": \"acme\",\n  \"planName\": \"free\",\n  \"ownerEmail\": \"owner@acme.com\",\n  \"ownerPassword\": \"SecureP@ss123\",\n  \"ownerFullName\": \"John Owner\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required.**\n\nCreates the business tenant, provisions its isolated PostgreSQL schema, and registers the first user as OWNER.\n\nTokens are returned as httpOnly cookies. The response body contains user + tenant info."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"SecureP@ss123\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required.**\n\nAuthenticates with email + password. Sets `access_token` and `refresh_token` as httpOnly cookies."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh tokens",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Rotates the token pair using the `refresh_token` cookie. Includes reuse detection — if the token was already consumed, all sessions are revoked."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "**Requires auth.**\n\nRevokes the current refresh token and clears all auth cookies. Returns 204."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "**Requires auth.**\n\nReturns the user decoded from the JWT cookie: id, email, role, tenantId, schemaName."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot-Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/forgot-password",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "forgot-password"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required.**\n\nAlways returns 204 regardless of whether the email exists (prevents user enumeration). Token expires in 30 minutes."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset-Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/reset-password",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "reset-password"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{reset_token}}\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewSecureP@ss123\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required.**\n\nConsumes the reset token (single-use) and sets the new password. Revokes all active sessions."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Google OAuth — initiate",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/auth/google?slug={{tenantSlug}}",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "google"],
              "query": [{ "key": "slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}" }]
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required.**\n\nRedirects to Google OAuth. Pass `?slug=your-tenant-slug` so the backend knows which tenant to authenticate against.\n\n> Open in browser — Postman cannot follow OAuth redirects."
          }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "Tenants",
      "description": "Tenant management. Most operations require ADMIN or OWNER role.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List all tenants",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/tenants",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["tenants"]
            },
            "description": "**Requires ADMIN.**\n\nReturns all active tenants."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get tenant by slug",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/tenants/{{tenantSlug}}",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["tenants", "{{tenantSlug}}"]
            },
            "description": "**Requires VIEWER.**\n\nReturns the tenant info by slug."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get tenant branding (public)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/tenant/{{tenantSlug}}/branding",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["tenant", "{{tenantSlug}}", "branding"]
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required.**\n\nReturns branding config: logo, favicon, company name, primary color, dark mode preference. Used by the frontend login page before auth."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get tenant theme CSS (public)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/tenant/{{tenantSlug}}/theme.css",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["tenant", "{{tenantSlug}}", "theme.css"]
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required. Cached 5 min.**\n\nReturns a CSS file with `:root` variables for colors, fonts, border radius, density, and icon pack."
          }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "Users",
      "description": "Team member management via invitation flow.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Invite team member",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/users/invite",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["users", "invite"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"sales@acme.com\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Sales Rep\",\n  \"role\": \"sales_rep\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Requires MANAGER or above.**\n\nSends an invitation email. Token expires in 72 hours.\n\nValid roles: `viewer` | `sales_rep` | `manager` | `admin`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Accept invitation",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/users/invite/accept",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["users", "invite", "accept"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{invite_token}}\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Sales Rep\",\n  \"password\": \"SecureP@ss123\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Public — no auth required.**\n\nValidates the invite token, creates the account, and returns an authenticated session (sets auth cookies). Token is consumed (single-use)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "Contacts",
      "description": "Full contact management with Colombian fields, full-text search, custom fields and timeline.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List contacts",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/contacts?page=1&limit=25",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["contacts"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "25" },
                {
                  "key": "q",
                  "value": "",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "description": "Full-text search (name, email, phone, document)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "new",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "description": "new | in_contact | qualified | client | inactive | lost"
                },
                {
                  "key": "source",
                  "value": "manual",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "description": "manual | whatsapp | web_form | referral | import"
                },
                {
                  "key": "tags[]",
                  "value": "vip",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "description": "Contact must have ALL specified tags"
                },
                { "key": "companyId", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "assignedToId", "value": "", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Requires VIEWER.**\n\nPaginated list with optional filters. All filters are AND-combined. `tags` uses `@>` — contact must have ALL specified tags."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get contact",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/contacts/{{contact_id}}",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["contacts", "{{contact_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "**Requires VIEWER.**\n\nReturns full contact including `customFields` (excluded from list for performance)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create contact",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/contacts",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["contacts"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Carlos\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Martínez\",\n  \"email\": \"carlos@empresa.com\",\n  \"phone\": \"3001234567\",\n  \"whatsapp\": \"3001234567\",\n  \"documentType\": \"cc\",\n  \"documentNumber\": \"1234567890\",\n  \"city\": \"Bogotá\",\n  \"department\": \"Cundinamarca\",\n  \"municipioCode\": \"11001\",\n  \"status\": \"new\",\n  \"source\": \"manual\",\n  \"leadScore\": 50,\n  \"tags\": [\"vip\", \"hot-lead\"],\n  \"customFields\": {\n    \"industry\": \"technology\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Requires SALES_REP.**\n\nDocument types: `cc` | `nit` | `ce` | `pp` | `ti`\n\nStatuses: `new` | `in_contact` | `qualified` | `client` | `inactive` | `lost`\n\nSources: `manual` | `whatsapp` | `web_form` | `referral` | `import`\n\n`municipioCode`: 5-digit DANE code (e.g. `11001` = Bogotá D.C.)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update contact",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/contacts/{{contact_id}}",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["contacts", "{{contact_id}}"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"qualified\",\n  \"leadScore\": 80,\n  \"tags\": [\"vip\", \"qualified\"],\n  \"customFields\": {\n    \"industry\": \"fintech\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "description": "**Requires SALES_REP.**\n\nAll fields are optional. Only provided fields are updated — patch semantics."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete contact (soft)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/contacts/{{contact_id}}",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["contacts", "{{contact_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "**Requires MANAGER.**\n\nSoft-deletes: sets `is_active = false`. Returns 204."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get contact timeline",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/contacts/{{contact_id}}/timeline",
              "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
              "path": ["contacts", "{{contact_id}}", "timeline"]
            },
            "description": "**Requires VIEWER.**\n\nReturns the contact's complete history: activities (last 50) and active deals. Fetched in parallel."
          }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "Settings",
      "description": "All tenant configuration. Most write operations require ADMIN.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "General",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Get general settings",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/settings/general",
                  "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
                  "path": ["settings", "general"]
                },
                "description": "**Requires VIEWER.**\n\nReturns full tenant settings: business info, i18n preferences, billing data, industry config, and current plan."
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Update general settings",
              "request": {
                "method": "PATCH",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/settings/general",
                  "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
                  "path": ["settings", "general"]
                },
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
                  "raw": "{\n  \"businessName\": \"Acme Corp\",\n  \"business\": {\n    \"phone\": \"6012345678\",\n    \"email\": \"info@acme.com\",\n    \"website\": \"https://acme.com\",\n    \"nit\": \"900123456\",\n    \"taxRegime\": \"responsible_iva\"\n  },\n  \"i18n\": {\n    \"language\": \"es\",\n    \"timezone\": \"America/Bogota\",\n    \"currency\": \"COP\",\n    \"dateFormat\": \"DD/MM/YYYY\",\n    \"numberFormat\": \"colombian\"\n  },\n  \"billing\": {\n    \"legalName\": \"Acme Corp S.A.S.\",\n    \"municipalityCode\": \"11001\",\n    \"fiscalResponsibilities\": [\"O-13\", \"O-15\"]\n  },\n  \"industry\": {\n    \"sector\": \"technology\"\n  }\n}"
                },
                "description": "**Requires ADMIN.**\n\nAll sections are optional — deep-merged with existing config.\n\nTax regimes: `responsible_iva` | `not_responsible` | `large_taxpayer` | `simple_regime`"
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Theme",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Get theme",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/settings/theme",
                  "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
                  "path": ["settings", "theme"]
                },
                "description": "**Requires VIEWER.**\n\nReturns the full theme config: colors, typography, branding, icon pack, dark mode."
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Update theme",
              "request": {
                "method": "PATCH",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/settings/theme",
                  "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
                  "path": ["settings", "theme"]
                },
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
                  "raw": "{\n  \"colors\": {\n    \"primary\": \"#6366F1\",\n    \"primaryForeground\": \"#FFFFFF\",\n    \"secondary\": \"#F1F5F9\",\n    \"accent\": \"#E0E7FF\",\n    \"sidebar\": \"#1E1B4B\",\n    \"sidebarForeground\": \"#FFFFFF\"\n  },\n  \"typography\": {\n    \"fontFamily\": \"inter\",\n    \"borderRadius\": \"md\",\n    \"density\": \"comfortable\"\n  },\n  \"branding\": {\n    \"companyName\": \"Acme Corp\",\n    \"logoUrl\": null,\n    \"faviconUrl\": null,\n    \"loginBgUrl\": null,\n    \"loginTagline\": \"Grow your business\"\n  },\n  \"iconPack\": \"outline\",\n  \"darkModeDefault\": \"system\"\n}"
                },
                "description": "**Requires ADMIN.**\n\nDeep-merges — only send the sections you want to change.\n\nFont families: `inter` | `roboto` | `poppins` | `nunito` | `system`\n\nBorder radius: `none` | `sm` | `md` | `lg` | `full`\n\nDensity: `compact` | `comfortable` | `spacious`\n\nIcon packs: `outline` | `filled` | `duotone` | `rounded`\n\nDark mode: `light` | `dark` | `system`"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Get theme history",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/settings/theme/history?limit=5",
                  "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
                  "path": ["settings", "theme", "history"],
                  "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "5", "description": "Max 10" }]
                },
                "description": "**Requires ADMIN.**\n\nReturns the last N theme changes with previous config snapshots (max 10, stored up to 30)."
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Restore theme from history",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{ "key": "x-tenant-slug", "value": "{{tenantSlug}}", "type": "text" }],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{NEXOURL}}/settings/theme/restore/{{history_id}}",
                  "host": ["{{NEXOURL}}"],
                  "path": ["settings", "theme", "restore", "{{history_id}}"]
                },
                "description": "**Requires ADMIN.**\n\nRolls back the theme to the state captured in the history record. Current state is saved to history before rolling back."
              }
            }
          ]
        },

